      • getKeyword

        public java.lang.String getKeyword()
        Description copied from interface: ITestStep
        Get's the Keyword to execute for this step. If Keyword = PageObject, the framework will look for the PageObject method specified in the Objects column using package.class.method syntax and attempt to execute the method providing no parameters If Keyword contains a '.' the framework will assume to execute a custom created keyword with the syntax of package.KeywordClass and look for a method on the keyword called 'instantiateExternal' and supply the given Excel column params to it
        Specified by:
        getKeyword in interface ITestStep
        Returns:
        String of the Keyword name to execute
        See Also:
        ITestRunner.runCustomKeyword(String, List, List)
